l in the finals.\", \"from\": 4376, \"to\": 4436, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"33] Imane\", \"from\": 4377, \"to\": 4386}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold medal\", \"from\": 4406, \"to\": 4420}, {\"ngram\": \"the finals\", \"from\": 4424, \"to\": 4434}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, she was disqualified shortly before her gold medal bout against People's Republic of China boxerYang Liu.\", \"from\": 4437, \"to\": 4551, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People's Republic\", \"from\": 4510, \"to\": 4527}, {\"ngram\": \"China\", \"from\": 4531, \"to\": 4536}]}, {\"sentence\": \"[citation needed]This disqualification happened three days after Khelif defeatedAzalia Amineva[ru], a previously unbeaten Russian prospect, restoring the Russian boxer's undefeated record.\", \"from\": 4551, \"to\": 4739, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4705, \"end\": 4712, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language_in_Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.6426804017878461, \"rank\": 0.5548226399809449, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language_in_Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language_in_Ukraine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"needed]This disqualification\", \"from\": 4561, \"to\": 4589}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif defeatedAzalia Amineva[ru\", \"from\": 4616, \"to\": 4648}]}, {\"sentence\": \"[34]The IBA claimed the disqualifications were based on unspecified \\\"gender tests\\\", which theInternational Olympic Committee(IOC) later determined were \\\"completely arbitrary\\\", \\\"illegitimate\\\", and \\\"lacked credibility.\", \"from\": 4739, \"to\": 4955, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4747, \"end\": 4750, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999999999663487, \"rank\": 3.375888511629139e-11, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbp